text: Brendon Reading (born 26 January 1989) is an Australian racewalker. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's 50 kilometres walk. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male racewalkers Category:Olympic athletes of Australia Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics
